title: 250: Craig Capurso- Why Compete?
description: Craig Capurso is back with the Mind Pump Crew! A lot has transpired since the last time Craig was on Mind Pump. Sal, Adam & Justin talk to Craig about fatherhood, the upcoming Men's Classics competition and Metron, Craig's company that uses data to mazimize training results. Please subscribe, rate and review this show! Learn more about Mind Pump at www.mindpumpmedia.com
